*** Test Cases ***
Valid Login
  Open Browser to Login Page
  Input Username    user1
  Input Password    User1_123
  Submit Credentials
  Dashboard Should Be Open
  [Teardown]      Close Browser
  
*** Keywords ***
  Open Browser to Login Page
  Open Browser      ${LOGIN URL}    ${BROWSER}
  Title Should Be   OWASP Node Goat

